00:25:31,439 --> 00:25:32,640
I think that

590
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:35,719
life is very short.

591
00:25:35,719 --> 00:25:36,640
Can be counted on one's fingers

592
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:39,479
and then use my heart to find the one

593
00:25:39,479 --> 00:25:42,599
who can broaden the horizon of my life

594
00:25:42,599 --> 00:25:43,479
that person,

595
00:25:43,479 --> 00:25:45,000
I think love is

596
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:48,280
to be yourself boldly and truly,

597
00:25:48,280 --> 00:25:49,160
and then

598
00:25:50,119 --> 00:25:51,199
go for it!

599
00:25:51,199 --> 00:25:53,719
Love is the game of the brave

600
00:25:53,719 --> 00:25:56,079
to love or not to love is the right of oneself and others.

601
00:25:56,079 --> 00:25:58,640
I love you, and you are free.

602
00:25:59,319 --> 00:26:01,800
Love will complete us.

